liveBlogPostPrepared.plaintext: The crowd doesn't need much more of a rev up now! A swinging delivery, Marnus defended but feathered the ball through to Baristow, who made a great catch low to his right. He prodded at it a bit, but a brilliant ball. He played that a bit too far away from his body did Marnus, not a great look on the replay.
liveBlogPostPrepared.title: EDGED! MARNUS GOES FOR A GOLDEN DUCK!

liveBlogPostPrepared.plaintext: That's a horrible shot from Warner, driving at a ball that should not be driven and he's played onto his own stumps. That's Warner gone for 9, Broad has him for the 15th time in Test cricket. Australia 1-29.
